ITV.Tour.de.France.2014.Stage.4.Live.PDTV.x264-NX

Tuesday 8th July 2014 ITV4
2pm to 5pm Live

Stage four sees the peloton back in France with another day for the sprinters. Racing inland from the start at the coastal resort of Le Touquet, the riders will tackle 164 more or less flat kilometres before finishing next to the brand new Pierre Mauroy Stadium in Lille. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary by Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting the reporter at the roadside.
